name: Flyboard#1
description:
Using Jetski's water propulsion, Flyboard gives strength to your feet and arms, while 80% of the pressurized water is given to your feet and 20% to your arms in the form of pressure. While this power given to your feet raises you up to 8-10 meters from the ground, the pressure on your arm helps you stay balanced.
